snippet.title: Captain Pawsome - announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1551000/Captain_Pawsome/

Set sail with Captain Pawsome on the relaxing 2D fishing adventure! Craft, upgrade, customize, and conquer the high seas. Clean the environment, catch unique fish, and unleash your inner adventurer. Dive in now and make a splash!
